WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:03.549
To reorder columns in a list using the Edit Columns dialog,

1
00:00:03.809 --> 00:00:06.650
open the List Actions menu using the gear icon,

2
00:00:06.929 --> 00:00:08.310
then select "Edit columns".

3
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:13.180
The columns currently displayed in the list appear on the right,

4
00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:15.159
in the "Selected columns" panel.

5
00:00:15.659 --> 00:00:19.860
Drag a column up or down in the list to change the order it appears from left to right.

6
00:00:25.120 --> 00:00:25.930
When you're finished,

7
00:00:26.040 --> 00:00:28.190
click "OK" to apply your changes.

8
00:00:29.809 --> 00:00:32.348
The columns now appear in the selected order.

9
00:00:32.729 --> 00:00:34.220
As with other list changes,

10
00:00:34.409 --> 00:00:38.029
this applies only to your personal view and won't affect what others see.
